    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it doesn't feel like a \"fresh start\" though. it feels like i'm just mourning someone who isn't coming back. like there is no \"new version,\" just the leftovers. the energy is gone. everything is just heavy and gray. it feels more like a burden to keep pretending i'm actually alive than anything else.",
